details.name: Dockyard Autocross
details.creator: opalescentfalcon
details.desc: Slalom in between the shipping containers and find the perfect line through the decreasing radius left turn to carry the most speed into the chicane. GP (Grand prix) style race made using cunning stunts props that can also be a drift circuit with muscles in rain. [ Press L1 at the end if you want to Bookmark. ]
